snippet.title: Interplanetary: Enhanced Edition launch trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/650220
Website: http://www.interplanetarygame.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/teamjollyroger
Twitter: https://twitter.com/teamjollyroger

Interplanetary: Enhanced Edition is a gravitational artillery strategy game, where players wage wars by developing their home planets and firing planetary barrages at the enemy planets.

Releasing on Steam on August 2nd, 2017. Available on Windows, Mac and Linux.
